## Implementation Plan

### Phase 1: Protocol Implementation
1. Implement Art-Net v2/v3 packet structure (OpCode, Universe, Data)
2. Implement sACN (E1.31) with CID, Universe, and DMP layers
3. Create UDP socket management with multicast support
4. Add network interface selection and configuration

### Phase 2: Universe Management
1. Create universe pool (allocate/free universes)
2. Implement universe data buffers (512 bytes per universe)
3. Add universe merging (HTP/LTP prioritization)
4. Create universe status monitoring

### Phase 3: Fixture Integration
1. Port fixture profile system (GDTF, custom JSON)
2. Implement channel mapping (DMX channel → fixture parameter)
3. Add RDM (Remote Device Management) support
4. Create fixture library management

### Phase 4: Performance & Reliability
1. Optimize for 44+ FPS DMX updates (22.7ms period)
2. Implement packet scheduling and timing
3. Add network redundancy (multiple NICs)
4. Create comprehensive error handling and recovery

### Phase 5: WebSocket & Control
1. Implement WebSocket handler for remote control
2. Create REST API for configuration
3. Add real-time monitoring dashboard
4. Implement live patching and override

### Phase 6: Testing & Validation
1. Unit tests for protocol packet creation
2. Integration tests with real DMX hardware
3. Network stress tests (packet loss, latency)
4. Compliance testing with Art-Net/sACN specifications

