## Inputs and Outputs

### Inputs

| Input | Source | Description |
|-------|--------|-------------|
| DMX data | Effects, controllers | 512-byte arrays per universe |
| Fixture definitions | Configuration files | GDTF, JSON profiles |
| Network config | User/UI | IP addresses, protocols |
| Control commands | WebSocket, REST API | Real-time control |

### Outputs

| Output | Destination | Description |
|--------|-------------|-------------|
| Art-Net packets | Network (UDP 6454) | DMX data via Art-Net |
| sACN packets | Network (UDP 5568) | DMX data via sACN |
| Status updates | Monitoring | FPS, packet loss, errors |
| WebSocket events | Remote clients | Real-time state changes |

---

## What It Does NOT Do

- ❌ Does **not** generate DMX data (effects provide data)
- ❌ Does **not** control fixtures directly (use FixtureProfiles)
- ❌ Does **not** provide RDM discovery (basic RDM only)
- ❌ Does **not** handle lighting design (use external software)
- ❌ Does **not** store DMX snapshots (use StateManager)
- ❌ Does **not** do timecode sync (use separate Timecode module)

