## Risks & Mitigations

| Risk | Likelihood | Impact | Mitigation |
|------|------------|--------|------------|
| Network packet loss | Medium | High | UDP with checksums, retransmission strategy |
| Timing jitter | Medium | High | Real-time scheduling, high-priority threads |
| Protocol compliance | Low | Medium | Wireshark validation, spec adherence |
| Firewall blocking | High | Medium | Document port requirements (6454, 5568) |
| Multi-controller conflicts | Medium | Medium | Priority system, merge strategies |

